text: Bandi Atai Khan (also known as Banda Atai Khan) is one of the 51 Union Councils of Abbottabad District in the Khyber Pakhtunkhwa province of Pakistan. == Location == Bandi Atai Khan is in the south of the district at 34°02'60"N, 73°13'0"E. It has a height of 1035 metres (3398 feet).Falling Rain Genomics – Location of Bandi Atai Khan ==References== Category:Union councils of Abbottabad District
